### Vulnerable Code Snippet

```java
// Vulnerable code snippet using unsafe input handling
public void handleUserInput(String input) {
    // This method is vulnerable because it directly uses user input without validation
    System.out.println("User input: " + input);
    // Further processing that could be vulnerable due to unvalidated input
    executeCommand(input);
}

public void executeCommand(String command) {
    // Executing a command without validation can lead to vulnerabilities
    // This is a bad practice and can be exploited by attackers
    Runtime.getRuntime().exec(command);
}
